​​No broker fee, low security deposit (on approved credit), 1 MONTH FREE ON SELECT UNIT.  No amenities fee. <br>
<br>
Great community in Hudson County with easy access to NYC in a full service building. Homes come with hardwood floors throughout both living space and bedrooms. Huge walk in closets with new stainless steel appliances.  Near the waterfront with plenty of restaurants, shops, cafes, and transportation in NY.                                                <br>
<br>
Amenities include:  24 hr fitness center, indoor garage, childrens play room, conference room, outdoor lounge with barbeque grills, swimming pool, in unit washer and dryer, and more! <br>
